WSJ FOE year 2 🤍
.
.
The last few months have been really crazy but I have to take a moment to appreciate my amazing experience this year at the Wall Street Journal’s Future of Everything Festival! Year 1 was great, year 2 was even better! I cannot even begin to describe how incredibly grateful I am that I was able to see incredible speakers like Michelle Obama, the heads of multiple Fortune 500 brands and restauranteurs like Éric Ripert, as well as try new products and cutting edge technology at Spring Studios! Additionally, the WSJ FOE team really did an amazing job curating unique experiences this year like the Festival Happy Hour with Michael Kors and Naomi Watts and Chef’s Tables at Le Bernadin, Don Angie and Tatiana. Looking forward to more years of the festival, meeting wonderful people and experiencing the future of everything!

خافو ما تعيشو وانتو عايشين...

ودايما و ابدا واثقة انه الله بيبعتلنا على قد مقدرتنا...و بيعرف انه نحن قد كل شي.. فليش نخاف من شي الله كاتبلنا ياه
